1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,140 --> 00:00:48,820
=Episode 8=
=Plan to Rewrite Fate Begins=

11
00:01:00,110 --> 00:01:01,520
Go get more people over here.

12
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:04,640
Let your guys have some fun first.

13
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:05,920
Yes, Ma'am.

14
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,560
So Mrs. Liu is doing this yourself?

15
00:01:10,590 --> 00:01:11,760
So this Li family

16
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:14,070
isn't as classy as I imagined.

17
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,230
Because...

18
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,920
I just really want to

19
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:20,150
see you completely taken down.

20
00:01:20,590 --> 00:01:22,430
Mrs. Liu, you really like thrills.

21
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:23,840
Otherwise,

22
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,710
you wouldn't be with Mr. Zhong.

23
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,310
What do you actually know?

24
00:01:30,230 --> 00:01:31,070
Speak!

25
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,680
That day, in Master Li's study,

26
00:01:34,230 --> 00:01:35,760
I saw how nervous Zhong was about you.

27
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:37,350
That's when I figured it out.

28
00:01:43,790 --> 00:01:44,950
If Ye Lang dies,

29
00:01:45,510 --> 00:01:47,120
it does Zhong no good at all.

30
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,640
But you're different.

31
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:51,040
If Ye Lang dies,

32
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,920
then your son, Li Hong,

33
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:54,590
stands to gain the most.

34
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,480
Let me guess.

35
00:01:57,230 --> 00:01:58,640
If I vanish here today,

36
00:01:58,950 --> 00:02:00,950
then the blame for your deal with

37
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,070
Zhong Minghui gets pinned on me?

38
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:07,840
Jiang Niannian.

39
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,680
Knowing too much

40
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,280
is exactly why you must die.

41
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:14,800
Since I'm about to die,

42
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:17,000
I have one last question.

43
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:19,560
Where is Jiang Xiaodi?

44
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,360
Where are you going?

45
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,640
Niannian is missing.

46
00:02:23,850 --> 00:02:25,080
I received this.

47
00:02:29,030 --> 00:02:30,310
You should take a look.

48
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:34,240
Brother, you should brace yourself.

49
00:02:43,010 --> 00:02:43,940
Beauty...

50
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,120
What is this?

51
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,710
She's the shameless woman

52
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,470
you brought home.

53
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:49,710
Do you know

54
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:52,430
Zhong was bewitched by her

55
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:54,240
into hurting you?

56
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,800
She wanted you dead

57
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,800
and to seize our fortune.

58
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,960
Young Master.

59
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:01,280
Today, a servant

60
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,080
found Ms. Jiang's underwear

61
00:03:03,490 --> 00:03:04,350
while cleaning

62
00:03:04,470 --> 00:03:05,630
Mr. Zhong's room.

63
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,240
No way!

64
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,430
I think you've

65
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,590
lost your head over desire.

66
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,240
Give Niannian back to me.

67
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:14,000
That woman

68
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:16,280
has already been dealt with.

69
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:17,920
I think

70
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:18,960
you also need

71
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,430
to be taught a lesson.

72
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,430
Bring in the family punishment.

73
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,960
Stop!

74
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,430
I have evidence

75
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,150
which can prove

76
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:45,590
Liu Yexi worked with Zhong Minghui

77
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,000
to hurt Ye Lang.

78
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:49,620
(Audio Recording)

79
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:54,710
If Ye Lang dies,

80
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:57,080
it does Zhong no good at all.

81
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,430
But you're different.

82
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,800
If Ye Lang dies,

83
00:04:01,310 --> 00:04:02,430
then your son, Li Hong,

84
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,190
stands to gain the most.

85
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,270
Let me guess.

86
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,280
If I vanish here today,

87
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:11,000
then the blame for your deal with

88
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:13,000
Zhong Minghui gets pinned on me?

89
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:14,150
Jiang Niannian.

90
00:04:14,710 --> 00:04:17,120
Knowing too much is exactly
why you must die.

91
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:18,670
Father,

92
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,160
I had nothing to do with this.

93
00:04:21,190 --> 00:04:22,920
That woman must've used AI

94
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:24,070
to fake mother's voice!

95
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:26,870
AI?

96
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,390
Since I'm standing here just fine,

97
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:32,070
then why not take a guess

98
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,070
who the woman in the video

99
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,400
really is?

100
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,150
Quick.

101
00:04:37,390 --> 00:04:39,310
Bring her back!

102
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,200
Father.

103
00:04:46,390 --> 00:04:47,270
Let me go.

104
00:04:47,670 --> 00:04:48,510
Let me go!

105
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,920
Let go of me!

106
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,510
Next week is my engagement ceremony with Xue.

107
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:58,310
On that day,

108
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,600
there will be shareholders, relatives

109
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:02,920
and reporters from all over Manlong.

110
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,270
Given Mom's condition...

111
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,830
Lock her

112
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:09,390
in a room.

113
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,390
Not a single word

114
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:16,120
of what happened today can be leaked.

115
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,720
I use myself

116
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,190
to help you bring down Liu Yexi.

117
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:22,590
Young Master,

118
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:24,710
time to pay up.

119
00:05:28,630 --> 00:05:29,470
Niannian.

120
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,870
Why do you need that much money?

121
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:32,920
Are you in trouble?

122
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:35,240
Just tell me.

123
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,750
I can help you fix anything.

124
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:40,720
(Who's using Xiaodi to threaten me?)

125
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,270
(Ye Lang.)

126
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,240
(Can I really trust you?)

127
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,830
Money, you know,

128
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:50,360
the more, the better.

129
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:52,110
Wait,

130
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,080
are you backing out?

131
00:05:57,460 --> 00:05:58,100
(Transfer)

132
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:58,580
(Successful)

133
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:05,240
Thanks for your business.

134
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:09,040
Now come get your reward.

135
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:16,960
Niannian.

136
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,040
I don't need anything from you.

137
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,000
Ye Lang.

138
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:29,720
Do you really love me?

139
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,560
I have no good education,

140
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:32,720
no good background.

141
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:34,560
You got rid of Jiang Qingqing,

142
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:36,000
but another girl will appear.

143
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:36,910
Jiang Niannian,

144
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,960
there has never

145
00:06:42,190 --> 00:06:43,070
been anyone else.

146
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,160
Only you.

147
00:06:48,020 --> 00:06:48,940
(Past and present,)

148
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,760
(I only want you.)

149
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,320
(Ye Lang.)

150
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,680
(If you were the first I met,)

151
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,600
(maybe we would've had a story.)

152
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:01,270
(But sadly,)

153
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,120
(you weren't the first.)

154
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:36,710
(Ye Lang.)

155
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:38,560
(Once I find Xiaodi, I'll leave.)

156
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,680
(True love is too risky.)

157
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:42,150
(I'm scared.)

158
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,880
Thank you.

159
00:08:30,190 --> 00:08:31,030
What is it?

160
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:32,440
One breakfast

161
00:08:32,670 --> 00:08:34,200
makes you this moved?

162
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:38,790
Breakfast doesn't matter.

163
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,870
Who I eat with does.

164
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,670
(Thank you for staying.)

165
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:50,870
(Thank you for making me feel)

166
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:54,120
(we can have a happy ending.)

167
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:58,790
(He's threatening me again.)

168
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:01,150
(But I will never sacrifice Ye Lang)

169
00:09:01,550 --> 00:09:02,510
(to save Xiaodi.)

170
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:05,510
The highway's jammed.

171
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:07,510
Take the service road.

172
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,860
It's fine if we're late.

173
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,360
(The one threatening me,)

174
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,510
(could it be her?)

175
00:09:25,060 --> 00:09:29,220
(Jiang Xiaodi is safe.)

176
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,350
Bro,

177
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:43,600
what's wrong with you now?

178
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,670
Want me to dissect you and check?

179
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,720
I'm just being careful.

180
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,480
For your good.

181
00:09:52,870 --> 00:09:53,910
Life and death are fate.

182
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:55,870
If I die, give my body to the hospital.

183
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,030
But if you die,

184
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,320
then you're mine.

185
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,390
You can't die.

186
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,160
If you do,

187
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:11,910
finish Jiang Xiaodi's treatment first.

188
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:14,200
I owe her a healthy brother.

189
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,840
This patient's surgery

190
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:17,910
is really interesting.

191
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,080
But...

192
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:21,350
Bro,

193
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,960
did you really have to

194
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,030
pick me up this early?

195
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:25,720
It's only one o'clock now.

196
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,330
(One o'clock.)

197
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:30,480
(The crash in my past life was at 1:15.)

198
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,440
(As long as I avoid that time...)

199
00:10:38,140 --> 00:10:40,860
(Outpatient Lobby)

200
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,390
(1:20.)

201
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,840
(The time of the accident has passed.)

202
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:51,960
Ye Lang.

203
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,080
Are you questioning my skills?

204
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:56,200
With me on Jiang Xiaodi's case,

205
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,240
the success rate is at least 75.9%.

206
00:10:58,670 --> 00:11:00,240
But that's still not 100%.

207
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:04,030
What if I can make it 100%?

208
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,720
I'll give you my body anytime.

209
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,420
Fine. Just wait.

210
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:39,060
(Previous Life)

211
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,750
How could this happen outside the hospital?

212
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:42,550
He's an Attending Physician here.

213
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,680
What happened?

214
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,340
Director Ye.

215
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:51,030
Dr. Zheng Lu died in a car crash.

216
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,840
He had a brain surgery scheduled today.

217
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,200
Without him,

218
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,550
we can't guarantee it'll work.

219
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:58,960
Zheng Lu?

220
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:02,360
Which patient's surgery?

221
00:12:02,550 --> 00:12:03,750
Jiang Xiaodi.

222
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:07,670
All right.

223
00:12:07,790 --> 00:12:08,750
Disperse.

224
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,790
Poor guy, he's still so young.

225
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,240
(In my previous life, Zheng Lu died,)

226
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,000
(so Xiaodi's surgery didn't happen.)

227
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:19,080
(He was later killed in the hospital.)

228
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:21,360
(Niannian and I became enemies.)

229
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:23,200
(In this life,)

230
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:26,150
(if Zheng Lu can do Jiang Xiaodi's surgery)

231
00:12:26,270 --> 00:12:27,110
(and save Xiaodi,)

232
00:12:28,390 --> 00:12:30,910
(then our ending can change.)

233
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:49,750
Don't worry.

234
00:12:50,140 --> 00:12:52,240
If I die before dissecting you,
I won't rest in peace.

235
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,720
You can't die.

236
00:12:57,510 --> 00:12:58,400
Come on.

237
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,550
I'll take you there.

238
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:04,750
You're really acting strange today.

239
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,240
Shall I cut you open for a check
before the surgery?

240
00:13:09,940 --> 00:13:12,460
(Outpatient Hall)

241
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,370
Hello.

242
00:13:14,390 --> 00:13:16,470
Excuse me, is Dr. Zheng Lu here?

243
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,030
Sorry, Dr. Zheng

244
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:19,270
has a surgery scheduled today.

245
00:13:19,630 --> 00:13:21,590
Registration and consults are on hold.

246
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:36,030
Watch out!

247
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:36,990
Watch out!

248
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,490
What's going on?

249
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:40,350
Ye Lang.

250
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:42,740
Knife!

251
00:13:46,170 --> 00:13:47,030
- Quack.
- Ye Lang.

252
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:48,360
Stop hurting people!

253
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,040
Niannian.

254
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,080
Are you okay?

255
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,680
I'm fine.

256
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,160
Your hand.

257
00:13:57,380 --> 00:13:58,340
Stop the bleeding first.

258
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,080
Does it hurt?

259
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:02,040
How could you block it with your hand?

260
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:04,800
It doesn't hurt.

261
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:06,360
You put your hand on mine,

262
00:14:06,830 --> 00:14:07,670
then it won't hurt.

263
00:14:07,790 --> 00:14:08,840
You're still grinning?

264
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,480
Did you hit your head too?

265
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,750
Nurse, please help stop his bleeding.

266
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,710
Director Ye, please come with me.

267
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:15,920
Mm.

268
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:24,200
Miss, please don't worry.

269
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,390
The nurse will handle it.

270
00:14:26,860 --> 00:14:28,300
(Zheng Lu)

271
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:30,470
You are...

272
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:32,030
Zheng Lu, Dr. Zheng?

273
00:14:32,750 --> 00:14:33,590
Yes.

274
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:34,670
Thanks for saving me.

275
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:37,030
I'm Chief Neurosurgeon at Renxin Hospital,

276
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:38,800
Zheng Lu.

277
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:39,830
Dr. Zheng.

278
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:40,720
I'm Jiang Niannian.

279
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:42,120
I came to see you today.

280
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,080
Me?

281
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,440
Yes.

282
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:50,720
Have you treated a patient

283
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:51,680
named Jiang Xiaodi?

284
00:14:51,910 --> 00:14:52,790
A brain tumor patient.

285
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,270
I see lots of patients.

286
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,160
I don't recall.

287
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:03,080
Jiang Xiaodi is your...

288
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,560
My younger brother.

289
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,150
We only have each other.

290
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:08,790
But now he's missing.

291
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,440
Dr. Zheng.

292
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:12,390
I'm not asking to repay a favor.

293
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,150
If I find Xiaodi,

294
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,030
could you treat him?

295
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:18,110
Don't worry.

296
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:19,480
Saving lives is a doctor's duty.

297
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:22,990
Thank you.

298
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:25,800
(Ye Lang.)

299
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:27,200
(You owe me again.)

300
00:15:30,030 --> 00:15:31,440
(What went wrong this time?)

301
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:34,840
(I avoided the time of the accident,)

302
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:38,910
(but a car still nearly hit him.)

303
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:42,030
(And there was even a stabbing,)

304
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:44,060
(something that never happened before.)

305
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,600
(So the fate can't be changed?)

306
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:55,200
Didn't you go to the pre-op meeting?

307
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:58,270
Jiang Xiaodi's exam report.

308
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:01,820
(Basic Info Jiang Xiaodi)

309
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,150
Some indicators are unstable.

310
00:16:03,790 --> 00:16:04,750
And his blood type

311
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:06,270
is rare.

312
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,200
I checked the blood bank,

313
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,510
insufficient supplies.

314
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:14,390
Even if you volunteer as a blood donor,

315
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,910
the surgery still has to be delayed.

316
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:19,270
(Zheng Lu survived,)

317
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:21,510
(but Xiaodi's surgery still fell through.)

318
00:16:22,470 --> 00:16:23,330
(No.)

319
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:24,960
(It feels like someone's behind this.)

320
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:28,320
(Could someone else have had a rebirth too?)

321
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:31,720
Useless fool!

322
00:16:31,980 --> 00:16:32,940
Why didn't you kill him?

323
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,280
How could you miss?

324
00:16:53,180 --> 00:16:59,770
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

325
00:17:01,580 --> 00:17:07,790
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

326
00:17:08,340 --> 00:17:15,340
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

327
00:17:16,090 --> 00:17:18,560
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

328
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:23,560
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

329
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:27,790
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

330
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:32,230
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

331
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:36,070
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

332
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:41,820
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

333
00:17:41,820 --> 00:17:46,140
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

334
00:17:46,180 --> 00:17:50,000
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

335
00:17:50,010 --> 00:17:54,500
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

336
00:17:54,530 --> 00:17:59,360
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

337
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:06,300
♪Life finds its way again♪
